<i>noun</i>: 참관 [참관], 관측 [관측], 관찰 [관찰], 관망 [관망], 감시 [감시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참관 [참관]</dt><br>
<dd>observation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 벌어지는 장소에 가서 그 일을 직접 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of going to an event and watching it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>관측 [관측]</dt><br>
<dd>1. observation</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 기계로 자연 현상을 자세히 살펴보아 어떤 사실을 짐작하거나 알아냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of guessing or finding out a fact of natural phenomena by using a machine or observing in detail with eyes.</dd><br>
<dd>2. assumption; guess</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 상황을 자세히 살피어 이후의 일을 짐작함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of guessing what will happen after observing in detail a certain fact or situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>관찰 [관찰]</dt><br>
<dd>observation; examination</dd><br>
<dd>사물이나 현상을 주의 깊게 자세히 살펴봄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of watching an object or phenomenon carefully and in detail.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>관망 [관망]</dt><br>
<dd>1. observation</dd><br>
<dd>형편이나 분위기 등에 간섭하지 않고 멀리서 보기만 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of just seeing from a distance, not intervening in the situation or circumstances.</dd><br>
<dd>2. observation</dd><br>
<dd>풍경 등을 멀리서 바라봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of seeing a landscape or other things from a distance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감시 [감시]</dt><br>
<dd>surveillance; observation; watch</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 단속하거나 상황을 통제하기 위하여 주의 깊게 지켜봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of monitoring closely to control a person or situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>